      <body>
         <div>
            <pb facs="1862_08_06_Kniffler_Kanagawa_von_Reimer_Co_Nagasaki_1.tif" n="envelope"/>
            <p>
               <seg rend="center">
                  <foreign xml:lang="en-EN">
                     <add style="textOrientation: upside-down" resp="unclear">
                        <hi rend="latintype">This letter was brought by <unclear reason="eccentric_ductus">Mr <persName ref="K00084">Gray</persName>
                           </unclear>
                           <lb/> a passenger pr. “<name type="ship" ref="K01691">St
                                        Louis</name>” + just given<lb/> some forward</hi>
                     </add>
                  </foreign>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="center">
                  <hi rend="latintype">Mess<hi rend="superscript">rs.</hi>
                     <orgName type="firm" ref="K01004">L. Kniffler &amp; Co.</orgName>
                     <lb/>
                     <placeName ref="K00525">Yokohama</placeName>
                  </hi>
               </seg>
               <add resp="other" style="writingMode: vertical-lr; textOrientation: sideways-right" place="marginRight">
                  <hi rend="latintype">1862<lb/>
                     <placeName ref="K00514">Nagasaki</placeName>
                     <date when="1862-08-06">6 Aug</date>
                     <lb/>
                     <orgName type="firm" ref="K01023">Reimer + Co.</orgName> in <choice>
                        <abbr>liq.</abbr>
                        <expan>Liquidation</expan>
                     </choice>
                     <lb/>R<hi rend="underline">
                        <date when="1862-08-18">18 Aug</date>
                     </hi>
                     <lb/>
                     <date when="1862-08-24">24 id.</date>
                  </hi>
               </add>
            </p>
            <pb facs="1862_08_06_Kniffler_Kanagawa_von_Reimer_Co_Nagasaki_2.tif" n="2"/>
            <p>
               <seg rend="right">
                  <hi rend="latintype">
                     <placeName ref="K00514">Nagasaki</placeName>
                     <date when="1862-08-06">6 Aug 1862</date>
                  </hi>
               </seg>
               <lb/>
               <seg rend="center">Herren <hi rend="latintype">Kniffler &amp; Co.<lb/>
                     <placeName ref="K00521">Kanagawa</placeName>
                  </hi>
               </seg>
               <lb/> Wir erlauben uns Ihnen einliegend<lb/> einige Rechnungen zum in <hi rend="latintype"> Casso</hi>
               <lb/> zu überreichen, und bitten Sie<lb/> uns die Summen nach Eingang<lb/> unter
                    Aufgabe an Ihr hiesiges<lb/> Haus, <hi rend="latintype">creditiren</hi> zu wollen.<lb/>
               <table rows="6" cols="5">
                  <row>
                     <cell>W<hi rend="superscript">m</hi>
                     </cell>
                     <cell>
                        <persName ref="K00085">Aspinall</persName>
                     </cell>
                     <cell> </cell>
                     <cell>$</cell>
                     <cell>5.40.</cell>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <cell>M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                     </cell>
                     <cell>
                        <persName ref="K00086">Keswick</persName>
                     </cell>
                     <cell> </cell>
                     <cell>＂</cell>
                     <cell>25.60.</cell>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <cell>M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                     </cell>
                     <cell>
                        <persName ref="K00087">Lever</persName>
                     </cell>
                     <cell> </cell>
                     <cell>＂</cell>
                     <cell>60._.</cell>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <cell>M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                     </cell>
                     <cell>
                        <persName ref="K00088">Crutchley</persName>
                     </cell>
                     <cell> </cell>
                     <cell>＂</cell>
                     <cell>48._.</cell>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <cell>＂</cell>
                     <cell>do</cell>
                     <cell> </cell>
                     <cell>＂</cell>
                     <cell>
                        <hi rend="underline">82.10</hi>
                     </cell>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <cell/>
                     <cell/>
                     <cell/>
                     <cell>＄ 221.-</cell>
                     <cell/>
                  </row>
               </table> ferner haben wir die Herren <hi rend="latintype">
                  <orgName type="firm" ref="K01065">Thorel &amp; Co.</orgName>
               </hi>
               <lb/> ersucht, Ihnen eine Summe für<lb/> uns auszuzahlen, womit Sie ebenso<lb/>
                    verfahren wollen.<lb/> Die Herren <hi rend="latintype">
                  <persName ref="K00087">Lever</persName> &amp;<persName ref="K00088">Crutchley</persName>
               </hi>
               <lb/> möchten möglicherweise Schwierigkeiten<lb/> machen wegen Bezahlung; in
                    welchem<lb/> Fall wir Sie bitten, die Rechnungen<lb/> durch den Englischen <hi rend="latintype">Consul</hi> ein<lb/> treiben zu lassen; der
                    einliegende<lb/>
               <choice>
                  <abbr>eng</abbr>
                  <expan>englische</expan>
               </choice> Brief, sagt das nöthige. </p>
            <pb facs="1862_08_06_Kniffler_Kanagawa_von_Reimer_Co_Nagasaki_3.tif" n="3"/>
            <p>
               <seg rend="right">freundlichst grüßend<lb/> Ihre<lb/>
                  <hi rend="latintype">
                     <orgName type="firm" ref="K01023">Reimer &amp; Co</orgName> in <choice>
                        <abbr>liq</abbr>
                        <expan>Liquidation</expan>
                     </choice>
                     <lb/>
                     <hi rend="underline">
                        <persName ref="K00083">E L Reimer</persName>
                     </hi>
                  </hi>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <pb facs="1862_08_06_Kniffler_Kanagawa_von_Reimer_Co_Nagasaki_4.tif" n="4"/>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
   <text type="translation">
        <!-- from page 2 to 4, as the envelope contains only English text -->
      <body>
         <pb facs="1862_08_06_Kniffler_Kanagawa_von_Reimer_Co_Nagasaki_1.tif" n="envelope"/>
         <pb facs="1862_08_06_Kniffler_Kanagawa_von_Reimer_Co_Nagasaki_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <p>Nagasaki 6th Aug 1862<lb/>Messrs. Kniffler &amp; Co.<lb/>Kanagawa<lb/>We are so free
                as to pass you <lb/> some invoices enclosed here for <lb/> cashing, and ask you to
                credit us<lb/> the sums after receipt by sending<lb/> them to your local house. <lb/>
            <lb/>
            <table>
               <row>
                  <cell>W<hi rend="superscript">m</hi>.</cell>
                  <cell>Aspinall</cell>
                  <cell/>
                  <cell>$</cell>
                  <cell>5.40.</cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell>M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>.</cell>
                  <cell>Keswick</cell>
                  <cell/>
                  <cell>＂</cell>
                  <cell>25.60.</cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell>M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>.</cell>
                  <cell>Lever</cell>
                  <cell/>
                  <cell>＂</cell>
                  <cell>60._.</cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell>M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>.</cell>
                  <cell>Crutchley</cell>
                  <cell/>
                  <cell>＂</cell>
                  <cell>48._.</cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell>＂</cell>
                  <cell>do</cell>
                  <cell/>
                  <cell>＂</cell>
                  <cell>
                     <hi rend="underline">82.10</hi>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell/>
                  <cell/>
                  <cell/>
                  <cell>＄ 221.-</cell>
                  <cell/>
               </row>
            </table> Furthermore, we have asked Messrs.<lb/> Thorel &amp; Co. to pay out to you
                a sum <lb/> for us, with which please proceed<lb/> in the same way. <lb/>Messrs.
                Lever &amp;Crutchley<lb/>might cause trouble regarding<lb/> payment; in which case
                we ask you <lb/>to have the English consul collect the <lb/> invoice amounts; the
                enclosed <lb/> Eng. letter states the necessary details. </p>
         <pb facs="1862_08_06_Kniffler_Kanagawa_von_Reimer_Co_Nagasaki_3.tif" n="3"/>
         <p>With most cordial greetings <lb/>Your<lb/>Reimer &amp; Co in liq<lb/>E L Reimer</p>
         <pb facs="1862_08_06_Kniffler_Kanagawa_von_Reimer_Co_Nagasaki_4.tif" n="4"/>
      </body>
   </text>
